CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: DeFi Development Corp. has adopted a treasury policy under which the principal holding in its treasury reserve on the balance sheet will be allocated to Solana (SOL). In adopting its new treasury policy, the Company intends to provide investors a way to access the Solana ecosystem. The Company's treasury policy is expected to provide investors economic exposure to SOL investment.
